    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpatterned Cut 是一款令人上瘾的动作反射游戏，带来了前所未有的体验。在未来风格的环境中与敌人战斗，突破你的极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/065eba6d0d982f826c0392e55f3ea4ee.poster.avif?t=1734512895\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/065eba6d0d982f826c0392e55f3ea4ee.webm?t=1734512895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/065eba6d0d982f826c0392e55f3ea4ee.mp4?t=1734512895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>演示版</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反射场景共由 5 个章节组成，总计 16 个关卡。试玩版包含第一章中的第二个关卡。此外，试玩版中没有剧情场景。试玩版提供一个排行榜，如果你想看到自己排名更高，那就挑战极限并添加到愿望清单中吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/4ce41a212bcd215bcbe4952ee7ac95e1.poster.avif?t=1734512895\" width=500 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/4ce41a212bcd215bcbe4952ee7ac95e1.webm?t=1734512895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317200/extras/4ce41a212bcd215bcbe4952ee7ac95e1.mp4?t=1734512895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧集逻辑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不觉得重复的节奏反射游戏很无聊吗？你不再需要记住特定的模式来完成关卡。Unpatterned Cut 为你提供了独特的体验，即使在同一个关卡中，每次重试也会有不同的模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                             </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
